    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Summary</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where you are alone, you repeat your daily life in a nonchalant and somewhat joyful manner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simulation game about maintaining civilization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The objective is to maintain civilization until the day when you can no longer move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player chooses the next action, and the character just repeats the action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After time passes, things begin to fade away, but as long as they are repeated, they will remain.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Estimated playing time</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 hour or less</p>",
